<div class="firstTitle">Signing up with 511PA</div>

<ol>
	<li>Creating an account is NOT mandatory on this website; however if you do, you&rsquo;ll be able to personalize your experience and receive traffic alerts.</li>
	<li>Select &lsquo;Sign Up&rsquo; from the menu options in the top right corner</li>
	<li>You can now sign up with either your email or phone number.</li>
	<li>Enter your information and click Sign up button. Verify your account by clicking on the confirmation link that will be sent to your email or SMS.</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>



