<div class="firstTitle">Creating an Alert for your Route</div>

<ol>
	<li>In the Manage My Routes table, find the route that you previously saved that you would like to create an alert for and click &lsquo;Create Alert&rsquo;.</li>
	<li>You will be redirected to the alert creation page. Enter the required information for your route, select a delivery option (email or SMS), and click &lsquo;Save&rsquo;.</li>
	<li>You will now be notified of any future events that affect your route.</li>
</ol>
